{"tid":253821,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有人成日話巴士比地鐵難預時間，究竟巴士有幾難預時間？","createTime":"2017-05-22T16:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T00:03:36.000Z","uid":105567,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58032ca63bb2c23e09f3bae379d29e403380d992","tid":253821,"uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T16:47:02.000Z","msg":"其實日日坐點會難預時間呀，人地有時間表架麻，而且坐地鐵上上落落又要轉來轉去，繁忙時間車門要開關幾次先開得車，我真係睇唔出地鐵點樣比巴士容易預時間？<br />\n 何況我諗唔明點解有d人明明屋企有直接巴士線返工，但係都要坐地鐵先安樂，地鐵跪低左結果就因為平時少坐巴士而唔識轉車，自己都跪低左係度。"},{"pid":"50a326dd2f866c1bee4e567db8218aac23baa19d","tid":253821,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T16:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b15f756ead7949f2ae1d9f67b6ff267a2de03b3","tid":253821,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T16:50:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.memesuper.com/1554b2f2aec4ca681d5b77a15b51f494_meme-of-black-guy-with-question-marks-memesuper-question-mark-face-meme_802-523.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.memesuper.com%2F1554b2f2aec4ca681d5b77a15b51f494_meme-of-black-guy-with-question-marks-memesuper-question-mark-face-meme_802-523.png&h=8afdbf0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44e39e34fc611dec52c005ebb0c7e0ff3413e0a0","tid":253821,"uid":52585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:03:36.000Z","msg":"睇名就知樓主假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}